## Slide 6: Feature Deep-Dive — Dashboard (Command Center)

### 🏠 The Home Screen That Works For You

| Feature | What It Does | Agentic Intelligence |
|---------|-------------|---------------------|
| **Agent Status Bar** | Green dot showing "Eva active — 3 tasks processing, 2 reminders queued, 1 cart ready" | Real-time agent activity feed |
| **Today at a Glance** | Horizontal swipeable critical cards (Chart Paper, Dad's BP Meds, Grocery Cart) | Each card shows auto-action status (🤖 Cart ready, 💊 Auto-refill, 🛒 Auto-order) |
| **Protected Focus Time** | Shield icon blocking 4-5 PM — "Eva declined 2 meeting requests for this block ✨" | Auto-declines meeting invites during guarded blocks |
| **Smart Autopilot Grid** | Rx Tracker (2 refills due) + Cart Ready (₹340 BigBasket order at 10 AM) | Medication tracking + grocery cart auto-merge |
| **Staff Status Cards** | Sunita (Maid) — On Leave Tomorrow • Ram (Driver) — Arriving 8:30 AM • Lata (Cook) — Meal plan sent ✓ | Each staff member has **Chat** and **Call** buttons |
| **Staff Chat Modal** | Full chat interface — messages simulated via Eva's WhatsApp agent with delivery confirmation | "Message delivered via WhatsApp ✓" |
| **Voice/Call Modal** | Click-to-call with WhatsApp integration, voice note option | "Connecting via WhatsApp..." |
| **Today's Flow Timeline** | Visual timeline with color-coded events (Work=purple, School=pink, Me=green, Home=yellow) | Each event shows agent reasoning note |
| **Add Task Modal** | FAB "+" button opens full modal: title, time, category chips (School/Home/Office/Groceries/Health/Logistics) | Tasks added to live timeline instantly |
| **Add Staff Modal** | Add new staff with name, role (Maid/Cook/Driver/Nanny/Gardener/Watchman), phone | Staff appears with chat/call buttons immediately |
| **Remove Items** | X button on timeline items and staff cards — remove anything live | Dynamic state management |
| **Motivational Quotes** | Rotating quotes: *"She believed she could, so she automated the rest."* | Emotional connection layer |

