## Slide 7: Feature Deep-Dive — Planner (Kanban Board)

### 📋 Mobile-First Task Management

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Dual View Mode** | Toggle between **List View** and **Kanban Board** with animated switch |
| **Mobile Accordion Kanban** | On phones (<600px), columns stack vertically as expandable/collapsible accordion sections — no horizontal cut-off |
| **Desktop Horizontal Kanban** | On wider screens, traditional horizontal scrollable columns |
| **4 Kanban Columns** | Backlog → This Week → Today → Done — full task lifecycle |
| **Task Cards** | Category tag (OFFICE/HOME/SCHOOL), effort weight (🪶 Light / ⚖️ Medium / 🪨 Heavy), assignee, due date |
| **Agent Cognitive Notes** | Each task shows Eva's reasoning: _"Revenue slides + projections — need Finance inputs"_ |
| **"Move to" Buttons** | One-tap progression: Move to This Week → Move to Today → Move to Done |
| **Filter Pills** | All Tasks · Home & Family · Workplace — instant filter toggle |
| **Workplace Tasks** | Purple briefcase badge on work tasks: "Prepare Q3 investor deck", "Submit sprint review slides", "Review PR #438" |
| **Cognitive Load Summary** | Live stats bar: Your Load (31) · Delegated (7) · Work Tasks (6) · Total (42) |
| **Smart Rebalancer CTA** | "Q3 Pitch Week detected — Eva shifted 3 home tasks to your partner and auto-handled 2 via vendors" |
| **Add Task Modal** | Full modal with: Title, Category chips (7 options), Column selector (Backlog/This Week/Today/Done), Effort level, Assignee (You/Husband/Eva Auto) |
| **Delete Tasks** | X button on every task card — remove with live count update |
| **Delegation Indicators** | Green ⚡ for auto-handled tasks, 👤 for personal tasks |

