| **Weekly Task Distribution** | Bar chart Mon-Sun with improved height and spacing — no label overlap |
| **Invisible Expense Tracker** | ₹19,080 total: Groceries ₹4,280, School ₹1,650, Maid ₹6,000, Driver ₹3,200, Medicines ₹2,100, Quick-commerce ₹1,850 |
| **Splitwise Settlement Modal** | Click "Generate Splitwise Settlement" → shows Your share (84%), Partner's share (16%), Fair 50-50 split, **Partner owes you ₹6,487** → "Send Settlement to Partner" |
| **Weekly Reflections** | 5 reflection cards: 12 hrs saved, 23 tasks completed, 8 work tasks shipped, 4 hrs me-time protected, 6 tasks auto-delegated |
