## Slide 12: Feasibility, Security & Tech Stack

### 🛠️ Technical Implementation

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | React Native (Expo) — cross-platform iOS/Android/Web |
| **Design System** | Custom theme with Quicksand + Fustat fonts, pastel color palette, glassmorphism cards |
| **State Management** | React useState hooks — fully reactive UI |
| **Navigation** | React Navigation with Bottom Tabs + Stack |
| **UI Components** | Custom [AppModal](file:///d:/Tanay%20IMP/Hackathons/CREATION/PrettyLittleBabies_CreAItion/frontend/src/components/ui/AppModal.js#16-66), [GlassCard](file:///d:/Tanay%20IMP/Hackathons/CREATION/PrettyLittleBabies_CreAItion/frontend/src/components/ui/GlassCard.js#5-19), [AppButton](file:///d:/Tanay%20IMP/Hackathons/CREATION/PrettyLittleBabies_CreAItion/frontend/src/components/ui/AppButton.js#6-48) component library |
| **Icons** | Feather Icons (consistent, lightweight) |
| **Charts** | Custom SVG gauge + native bar charts (no heavy charting library) |

### 🔗 External API Integrations (Future Scope)

| API | Purpose | Status |
|-----|---------|--------|
| **Google Calendar API** | Sync events, detect collisions, auto-block focus time | 🟡 Planned |
| **Gmail API** | Auto-draft reschedule emails, parse forwarded itineraries | 🟡 Planned |
| **WhatsApp Business API** | Parse group messages, send staff messages in regional languages | 🟡 Planned |
| **Zepto / BigBasket API** | Auto-add items to cart, price comparison, scheduled delivery | 🟡 Planned |
| **Apollo Pharmacy / 1mg API** | Medication refill tracking, auto-reorder prescriptions | 🟡 Planned |
| **Swiggy / Zomato API** | Meal planning integration, auto-order based on cook's leave | 🟡 Planned |
| **Google Maps API** | GPS-based family tracking (husband near school for pickup) | 🟡 Planned |
| **Twilio / MSG91** | OTP verification, voice notes, call routing | 🟡 Planned |
| **Razorpay / UPI** | Auto-pay staff salaries, vendor bills, utility payments | 🟡 Planned |
| **Google Translate API** | Multi-language staff messaging (Hindi, Marathi, Tamil, etc.) | 🟡 Planned |
| **OpenAI / Gemini API** | NLP for WhatsApp parsing, voice transcription, task classification | 🟡 Planned |
| **Slack API** | Work status sync, auto-draft handover notes, OOO management | 🟡 Planned |

### 🔒 Security Considerations

| Area | Approach |
|------|----------|
| **Data Privacy** | End-to-end encryption for family data, staff contacts, financial information |
| **Authentication** | OTP-based phone verification (no passwords to remember) |
| **Budget Guardrails** | Auto-orders only within pre-approved budget thresholds |
| **Agent Transparency** | Every autonomous action shows reasoning — user can accept/reject |
| **GDPR/DPDP Compliance** | Minimal data collection, user-controlled deletion, consent-first approach |
| **Staff Data Protection** | Staff phone numbers encrypted, used only for authorized communication |

